            "stat_suffix": "min",
            "stat_qualitative": false,
            "body": "In controlled PPE testing, <strong>in-glove humidity exceeded 90% within 5–7 minutes on the back of the hand.</strong> Inside sealed gloves, wet skin changes what gets through.",
